        Crush SEO with A+ web vitals. Works with any javascript framework and infinitely extendable with any NPM package.
      </Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>
  </Container>

  <ContainerFW>
    <FeaturesGrid />
  </ContainerFW>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionHeadImg>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        6+ years experience optimising Shopify and Shopify Plus.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Shopify is one of the most powerful tools to revolutionise the e-commerce development space. We absolutely recommend using the platform in certain situations.
        For businesses that need secure, instant inventory management and other global scale goal requirements. Book in a call and hear how we would initially improve your store. 
        For a free simple 15 minutes of your time, we'll give away a few of our best tricks you can implement yourself straight away, as well as let know of a few serious customisations 
        we can apply with our development and design experience.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={Pagecover}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionHeadImg>
  </ContainerXL>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionHeadSecImg>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        21-day turnaround.
      </Fragment>
